        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Advanced Placement coursework reported may be posted to your transcript after being evaluated by your academic advisor. Acceptance of AP coursework is determined by the governing department and subject to change without notice. Advance Placement coursework accepted only for specific courses.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.slu.edu/office-of-the-university-registrar-home/academic-catalogs" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

 <p class="box-padding-3">
    Additional restrictions and requirements may apply to the policy listed below. For more detailed information, visit the college's AP policy on the Web or contact the college directly.
 </p>

